subject: Football
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: For the first time since October 2003, half of the top-10 teams in the Associated Press poll lost: No. 3 Oklahoma, No. 4 Florida, No. 5 West Virginia, No. 7 Texas and No. 10 Rutgers.
